 snekkerarbeider, tomt og grunnmursarbeider har det s\u00e5 langt kostet meg ca 700 000 kroner, sier hun stolt og forn\u00f8yd."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|sortrondelag"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "6f4c10516d3b85c9cdaf042bd1fc17adf18809da06cf31d29221afc4d98e4589"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-05-02T03:08:45.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Huset skulle rives, men firebarnsmammaen tok grep og s\u00f8rget for et nytt og varig hjem for seg og barna."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article9831289.ece/ALTERNATES/w980-default/flytting.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/9908fb0e6a5b30074a17158d54c10379f15fcbc8.jpg?59728aac"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["Dette \u00abflyttelasset\u00bb skapte 17.mai-stemning i \u00c5fjord -adressa.no", "En id\u00e9 tar form", "Vanskelig \u00e5 finne fagfolk", "Rasutsatt tomt", "- M\u00e5tte nesten gr\u00e5te"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "9908fb0e6a5b30074a17158d54c10379f15fcbc8"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["utenriks", "innenriks", "trondheim", "E6", "midtbyen", "bybrann", "bilulykker"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "utenriks,innenriks,trondheim,E6,midtbyen,bybrann,bilulykker"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "sortrondelag"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "home-and-garden"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": "hus"}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["nordtek", "kysthotellet", "oddveig forfot", "stokk\u00f8ya", "\u00e5rnes og monstad"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": ["r\u00f8ros", "verdal", "\u00e5fjord", "\u00e5rnes"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": "\u00f8ystein sivertsen"}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": ["nyheter", "nyheter/sor